OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be largely cloudy
OL,6,Fthroughout the day with some showery
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain to start. These
OL,8,Fshowers may turn heavy at times in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight with some
OL,13,Fshowery outbreaks of rain, heavy at
OL,14,Ffirst, gradually easing overnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FDull and cloudy through the
OL,17,Fmorning with a few light showers. Some
OL,18,Fbrighter spells may develop later in
OL,19,Fthe day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
