OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FDry
OL,6,Fstart Monday with some bright spells,
OL,7,Fthen rain for a time later. Bright
OL,8,Fspells and a few showers through
OL,9,FTuesday and Wednesday. Remaining quite
OL,10,Fcool.
